title: Packers-Chiefs, Browns, year of the Coach, and where Colin was right & wrong
itunes:title: Packers-Chiefs, Browns, year of the Coach, and where Colin was right & wrong
description:
Colin discusses the Packers-Chiefs game, the reasons the Browns are a mess and why their fans will soon be obnoxious again, why this NFL season is the year of the Coach, and where he was right and wrong over the weekend. Guests include Doug Gottlieb, Trent Dilfer, and Bucky Brooks.
